<br>
I dunno, you can get down to about 10 int or less by drinking... alot... and i sure as heck have more than:<br>
<br>
(10/5 + 0) * 60 + 60 = 2*60 + 60 = 180 mana<br>
<br>
or<br>
<br>
(10/5 + 0) + 120 = 122 mana <br>
<br>
i have cast an evac spell while totally drunk, and naked (300 mana) so there must be another equation<br>
